---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout
  title="About"
  description="About Md. Ifte Kharul Islam, engineering approach, values, and professional direction."
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow" data-reveal>About</span>
      <h1 data-reveal>Engineering style: practical, calm, and outcome-focused</h1>
      <p data-reveal>
        I enjoy building software that users can rely on repeatedly. My approach prioritizes clear product value,
        maintainable implementation, and disciplined execution over unnecessary complexity.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container hero-grid">
      <article class="surface-card" data-reveal>
        <img
          src="/images/user.jpg"
          alt="Portrait of Md. Ifte Kharul Islam"
          style="width: 100%; border-radius: 1rem; aspect-ratio: 4 / 5; object-fit: cover;"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </article>

      <article class="surface-card prose" data-reveal>
        <h2>What I optimize for</h2>
        <p>
          I focus on software quality that users can feel: fewer friction points, cleaner flows, and stable behavior
          over time.
        </p>
        <p>
          I value collaboration between product and engineering teams, and I prefer communication that is direct,
          respectful, and execution-oriented.
        </p>

        <h2>Current direction</h2>
        <p>
          My current direction is to keep deepening product engineering strength across mobile platforms and backend
          systems, while building reusable patterns for reliable feature delivery.
        </p>

        <h2>Certifications and profiles</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>ITEE FE Exam (October 2023)</li>
          <li>
            Codeforces profile:
            <a href="https://codeforces.com/profile/ifte_102" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">ifte_102</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            LeetCode profile:
            <a href="https://leetcode.com/u/iftekharul/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">iftekharul</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
